The paper deals with online matrix completion, a problem commonly studied in machine learning and optimization. The use of side information is also a common theme in these fields. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also involves optimization techniques and theoretical analysis, which could place it in cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) or cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms).
